### Verify credentials → should return valid: true
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/internal/platforms/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{"api_key": "my-key", "api_secret": "my-secret"}

###

### Market status → is_open: true
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/market/status
API-KEY: my-key
API-SECRET: my-secret

###

### Stocks → should return ARKA
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/market/stocks
API-KEY: my-key
API-SECRET: my-secret

###

### Place an order
POST http://localhost:8085/api/v1/orders
API-KEY: my-key
API-SECRET: my-secret
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform_user_id": "user-123",
  "instrument_type": "STOCK",
  "instrument_id": "ARKA",
  "order_type": "LIMIT",
  "side": "BUY",
  "quantity": 10,
  "limit_price": 129.00,
  "expires_at": "2025-12-31T23:59:59"
}

###

### Order book → should show the order above in bids
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/market/stocks/ARKA/orderbook
API-KEY: my-key
API-SECRET: my-secret

###

### Invalid ticker → should return 404 with error code
GET http://localhost:8085/api/v1/market/stocks/FAKE
API-KEY: my-key
API-SECRET: my-secret

###

### Update an option contract (all fields optional)
PUT http://localhost:8085/api/v1/admin/options/{optionId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "strike_price": 150.00,
  "expiry_time": "2025-12-31T23:59:59",
  "premium": 5.50,
  "is_active": false
}